35:20.857 --> 35:22.946
I am so sorry, I didn't
mean to scare you at all.

35:22.990 --> 35:26.907
I just, no, I came because
I didn't want you to be alone.

35:28.430 --> 35:30.171
Not like that.

35:30.215 --> 35:32.608
