too beep-boop-boppy for you,

37:43.609 --> 37:45.045
reach out to Soraya.

37:45.088 --> 37:47.526
She's on our side. Okay, bye.

37:47.569 --> 37:48.875
Oh.

37:48.918 --> 37:52.008
I'm just kidding. Um...

37:52.052 --> 37:54.707
I mean, this is goodbye.

37:54.750 --> 37:58.841
Um, and I'm...
I'm sorry it sucks, but...

37:58.885 --> 38:02.802
this would've been way too hard
to do in person, so...

38:02.845 --> 38:06.849
Uh, but at least
