39:31.543 --> 39:33.762
Heavens, why? I'm good.

39:33.806 --> 39:35.547
I don't know
if that is true,

39:35.590 --> 39:38.158
given your recent outbursts.

39:38.201 --> 39:40.465
I find them
rather alarming, dear.

39:40.508 --> 39:42.380
I don't understand. I-I haven't
done nothing but offer you

39:42.423 --> 39:44.382
