in helping women like yourself--

39:47.472 --> 39:51.084
women with divergent
thinking-- get back on track.

39:51.127 --> 39:52.999
Jimmy, I-I don't need
no help thinking. I...

39:53.042 --> 39:54.348
It will only be a few months.

